I"I<p>This page is a summary of our work-life balance where we engage in shenanigans and we will be adding to it as we grow as a group.</p>

<h1 id="set-the-base-directory">Set the base directory</h1>
<p>base_dir=”$HOME/website/fun/imgs”</p>

<h1 id="loop-through-directories-that-contain-2023-in-their-names">Loop through directories that contain “2023” in their names</h1>
<p>for directory in “$base_dir”/2023*; do
    # Extract just the folder name
    dir_name=$(basename “$directory”)</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code># Loop through all .jpg images in the directory
for image in "$directory"/*.jpg; do
    # Extract the filename
    image_name=$(basename "$image")

    # Print the HTML tag
    echo "&lt;img src=\"/fun/img/$dir_name/$image_name\" style=\"max-height: 250px\"&gt;"
done done
</code></pre></div></div>

